    • assignLevel

      public void assignLevel(Problem problem)
      Assigns a level to the agent based on the given problem. If the agent has already seen the problem before, the level is set to "SAVEY." If the agent's department matches the problem's department, the level is randomly selected from the levels "SAVEY" and "DEFULT." Otherwise, the level is randomly selected from all available levels.
      Parameters:
      problem - The Problem object for which the level is to be assigned.
